			Scientist: {
				TownNPCMood: {
					HateBiome: I hate {BiomeName}, because it's too humid and there are way too many things trying to hurt you!
					DislikeBiome: I don't like {BiomeName}.
					LikeBiome: I like {BiomeName}. There is something soothing about the sound of the waves.
					LoveBiome: My body is made of white goo, so I fit in perfectly in {BiomeName}.
					HateCrowded: I can't get anything done with so much noise around me.
					DislikeCrowded: It's hard to concentrate with all those people around me.
					LoveSpace: It's nice not having so many people around me so I can concentrate.
					FarFromHome: I miss my desk and my equipment.
					NoHome: I am not a field researcher, so I would like to have a decent place to live.
					Content: I am doing just fine.
					# Nurse
					LoveNPC: I highly admire {NPCName} for curing all sorts of ailments.
					# Furry girl
					LikeNPC: I know from personal experience how painful a transformation can be, so seeing how well {NPCName} is putting up with it is quite impressive.
					# Wizard
					DislikeNPC: As a scientist I try to understand things, but I don't get what {NPCName} does and I don't like it.
					# Arms Dealer
					HateNPC: I really hate {NPCName} for selling the same weapons that were used in the riots.
					LikeNPC_Princess: "{NPCName} is always so cheerful, it's contagious."
					Princess_LovesNPC: "{NPCName} is always so cheerful, it's contagious."
				}

				DisplayName: Scientist
				Description: A scientist who previously worked on a cure for a deadly virus.
				Census.SpawnCondition: Behemoth defeated
			}

